<--!
When Dynamic Contrast Range (DCR) is enabled in the OSD:   
- Brightness and contrast cannot are disabled.
- Color menu is disabled (color related features)
- Scaling
- DisplayPort version selection is disabled 


When Low Blue Light feature is enabled in the OSD: 
- Brightness and Contrast unaffected, Color unaffected
- Scaling disabled
- DisplayPort version selection is disabled

When both are enabled:
- Brightness and contrast cannot are disabled.
- Color menu is disabled (color related features)
- Scaling
- DisplayPort version selection is disabled 

-->